    <div class="container" style="padding-left: 5%">
        <h2 style="color:olive">About us.</h2>
        <hr style="color: #683A0C" />
        <p>
            TempJobs.com is a two way bridge between thousands of job seeking people and home owners or small businesses that
            have jobs to be done within a short period of time. 
        </p>
            Employers can view profiles of many job seekers with various informal skills that employers may be looking for.
            Employers can also search for people based on informal skills they have and their residential areas.

            Employers can find job seekers with various skills that include dog walking, cutting trees, washing, ironing, working in the garding and many more.
        <p>
            Employers can post jobs and job seekers will view the job post and indicate their interest for the job.
            The employer can later view interested job seekers and select the ones they want.
            Job seekers have an option to employ multiple employees for a job.
        </p>
        <p>
            With the highest employment rate in south africa, TempJobs is an attempt to reduce the unemployment rate by giving job seekers a chnce
            to make money to make a living while they are still looking for long term employments.
        </p>
